係黃偉文根本寫緊自己 只不過係e神唱<br />\n你話首歌係e神自己填詞就話會令人代入首歌以e神角度去諗姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通首阿牛 e神又想過搶新娘啦喎？<br />\n新娘係邊個？搵返首歌邊年出。出個年又邊個結婚。睇下e神愛邊個多過佢老婆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f535812dd002bb721625797559347d893fcca47","tid":274981,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你地係咪諗多咗？?講埋人地老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最簡單係黃偉文根本寫緊自己 只不過係e神唱<br />\n你話首歌係e神自己填詞就話會令人代入首歌以e神角度去諗姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通首阿牛 e神又想過搶新娘啦喎？<br />\n新娘係邊個？搵返首歌邊年出。出個年又邊個結婚。睇下e神愛邊個多過佢老婆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n套戲同首歌都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc209904127e57a12c5ac295b8eaf3566abb35c5","tid":274981,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最愛這　這古老擴音機<br />\n是那動聽聲音　那缺憾美<br />\n再沙啞也帶著不羈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI would call you up every Saturday night<br />\nAnd we both stayed out 'til the morning light<br />\nAnd we sang, &quot;Here we go again&quot;<br />\nAnd though time goes by<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c58b37f34bb33105af9bed577d8558f62f0aed","tid":274981,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最痴線係eason 1974年出世<br />\n歌詞又真係話為何未及時地出生在1874 剛剛早一百年一個世紀<br />\n暗示eason對自己婚姻唔滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係eason嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就真係痴線啦 戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15f4972624ca0e4608511b4c2fde06841647019","tid":274981,"uid":743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"captain Bucky <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfb93c9f5520c4c66d8e3fc7caf846acfb7cf60","tid":274981,"uid":41302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"首歌唔係講套戲架咩<br />\n<br />\n可能直必左"},{"pid":"5359017dc17d7e8ad5b6c1eab91559eb9d2bd00c","tid":274981,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"講緊套戲呀"},{"pid":"9a7e5e572a37d2ebf936da5001747caa152e4f55","tid":274981,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"<